The class below fails with InvalidClassException after a new field is added. Fix it. Also: Logger and connection fields should not be serialized.
```java
class OrderService implements Serializable {
    private String orderId;
    private Logger log = Logger.getLogger("orders");
    private Connection dbConn;
    private int version; // newly added field
}
```

